## Properties {#properties}

### Style Properties

| Name | Default | Type | Description |
| ---- | ------- | ---- | ----------- |
| **`justifyContent`** | `MainAxisAlignment.START` | [==`MainAxisAlignment`==](#main-axis-alignment) | The main (vertical) axis alignment (the `justify-content` Flexbox property). |
| **`alignItems`** | `CrossAxisAlignment.STRETCH` | [==`CrossAxisAlignment`==](#cross-axis-alignment) | The cross (horizontal) axis alignment (the `align-items` Flexbox property). |
| **`reverse`** | `false` | `boolean` | Whether to reverse the direction of the flex axes. |

