## Related Objects {#related-objects}

The following objects are available as named exports in `'attractions/layout'`.

### `MainAxisAlignment` {#main-axis-alignment}

| Field | Description |
| ----- | ----------- |
| **`START`** | Pack items tightly at the start of the main axis. |
| **`CENTER`** | Pack items tightly in the center of the main axis. |
| **`END`** | Pack items tightly at the end of the main axis. |
| **`SPACE_AROUND`** | Create an equal amount of space on each side of each item. |
| **`SPACE_BETWEEN`** | Space out every item at an equal distance, spanning the entire main axis. |
| **`SPACE_EVENLY`** | Space out every item at an equal distance, making the same distance before the first and after the last item. |

### `CrossAxisAlignment` {#cross-axis-alignment}

| Field | Description |
| ----- | ----------- |
| **`START`** | Align all items at the start of the cross axis. |
| **`CENTER`** | Center all items within the Column. |
| **`END`** | Align all items at the end of the cross axis. |
| **`STRETCH`** | Make each item span the entire length of the cross axis. |
| **`BASELINE`** | Align all items by the baseline of their inner text. |

